<h4 id="org401d07e">Sqlite dired</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org401d07e">
<p>
In <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/emacs/comments/rlwipm/comment/hpjo30x">this</a> post a reddit user was kind enough to share a snippet to do just this
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-emacs-lisp">(<span style="font-weight: bold;">when</span> (functionp 'sqlite-available-p)
  (<span style="font-weight: bold;">require</span> '<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">sqlite-mode</span>)
  (<span style="font-weight: bold;">defun</span> <span style="font-weight: bold;">sqlite-file-p</span> ()
    (<span style="font-weight: bold;">let*</span> ((ms <span style="font-style: italic;">"SQLite format 3"</span>)
           (msl (length ms)))
      (<span style="font-weight: bold;">and</span> (&gt; (point-max) msl)
           (string= (buffer-substring 1 (1+ msl))
                    ms))))
  (<span style="font-weight: bold;">defun</span> <span style="font-weight: bold;">sqlite-mode-open-file*</span> ()
    (<span style="font-weight: bold;">let</span> ((f (buffer-file-name)))
      (kill-buffer (current-buffer))
      (sqlite-mode-open-file f)))
  (add-to-list 'magic-mode-alist '(sqlite-file-p . sqlite-mode-open-file*)))
</pre>
